\begin{frame}[c]{Manage your (external) Dependencies}

I love packages, I really do, but they will get you in trouble eventually. Use any of:

\begin{itemize}
\item Docker (any language)
\item renv (R)
\item virtual env (Python)
\item Guix (even nerdier than Docker)
\end{itemize}

\end{frame}

\begin{frame}[c]{Manage your (internal) Dependencies}

You only use the included toy data sets in R? Lay back and relax.\\
Oh, you work with real data. Use any of:

\begin{itemize}
\item Make (any language)
\item drake/targets (R)
\item doit (Python)
\end{itemize}

\end{frame}

